					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">If you are trying to use it to store a value in the code, you would do something like:
<br />
<br />LDA #$20  ; or whatever value you want
<br />STA p1_X  ; its stored
<br />
<br />LDA could be LDX or LDY &amp; STA would change to the corresponding X or Y
<br />
<br />Of course if you are doing some calculations and need to store that value, you wouldn't need the LDA part.</div>

